                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-670" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD BAKER</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> It was found in the place it had been in before—it is my umbrella, and the one which was missed from the hall.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I met a person who told me to ask if a person named Richardson worked there; I did so; when I came out of the house the man said I had stolen an umbrella; I know nothing about it.</p>
